I"<h3 id="what-does-it-take-to-build-a-design-system"><strong>What does it take to build a Design System?</strong></h3>

<p>They’ve been proven to help teams drive faster development, eliminate inconsistency, save money and reduce knowledge silos. Un-arguably, it’s a win-win situation. But how do you get started? We’re proud to present an descriptionductory guide to Design Systems, created to remove the overwhelming overhead a task like this can have.</p>

<h3 id="what-youll-learn">What you’ll learn</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>The basic principles</strong> of Design Systems, with their complexities de-mythed.</li>
  <li><strong>Why Design Systems matter</strong>, from preventing inconsistencies, simplifying processes for future projects and harmonising your products.</li>
  <li><strong>Best practice</strong> for you and your team to get started in building a successful Design System.</li>
  <li><strong>Exposé on the Design System behind Marvel</strong>, learn more about the workflow that works for us.</li>
</ul>
